  "title": "ADHOC ASSISTANT STUDENT CARE TEACHER",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct both indoor and outdoor activities for primary school      students</li>\n  <li>Ensure  students' welfare and safety are being taken care of</li>\n  <li>Supervise students to ensure completion of homework and that spelling revision is done</li>\n  <li>Support in dismissal duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min.  GCE “O” level and above</li>\n  <li>Able  to lead and manage primary school students</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Passion working with primary school students</li>\n  <li>Able to commit at least 3 weekdays a week</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>WORKING HOURS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Usually 12.30pm to 6.30pm (weekdays)</li>\n</ul>",
